Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.85,0:22:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll get right to the point!\NAren't you going to get married?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.18,0:22:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Also, your habit of always being late\Nwhen your team assembles.
